# Refine TODO Tab and Fix Redraw Logic

This plan addresses issues with the TODO tab integration, layout stability, and redraw failures when switching tabs.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> - **Full Migration:** The [TodoPanel](file:///Users/caishanghong/Shopify/cli-tool/llxprt-code-4/packages/cli/src/ui/components/TodoPanel.tsx#26-30) and detailed Todo tool outputs must be **removed** from the `MainChat` tab and exclusively rendered in the [TodoTab](file:///Users/caishanghong/Shopify/cli-tool/llxprt-code-4/packages/cli/src/ui/components/tabs/TodoTab.tsx#14-31). `MainChat` should only display minimal summaries if necessary, keeping the interface clean and stable.
> - **Redraw Fix:** Switching tabs will trigger a full terminal clear and static re-render to ensure a clean UI state.

